sequenceDiagram
    participant Inspector as Financial Authority/Inspector
    participant TSE as TSE
    participant Storage as Storage Medium

    Inspector->>TSE: exportLoggingCertificates()<br/>(no authentication required)
    activate TSE
    
    TSE->>TSE: Get current Certificate Chain
    
    TSE->>TSE: Collect Certificates:<br/>- TSE Certificate<br/>- Intermediate CA Certificates<br/>- Root CA Certificate
    
    alt Certificates not available
        TSE-->>Inspector: Exception:<br/>ErrorExportLoggingCertificateFailed
    else Certificates available
        TSE->>TSE: Pack TAR Archive:<br/>only Certificates (*.crt)
        
        TSE->>TSE: Generate Filename:<br/>[SERIALNUMBER]_certificates.tar
        
        TSE-->>Inspector: TAR Archive + Filename
    end
    deactivate TSE
    
    Note over Inspector: Smaller Archive,<br/>only Certificates<br/>(no Log Messages)
    
    Inspector->>Inspector: Extract Certificates
    Inspector->>Inspector: Validate Certificate Chain
    Inspector->>Inspector: Check Validity & Revocation
